## futon3c Buildout (P12–P16)

The following prototypes capture the major futon3c systems that were built
after the three-futon split. They are recorded here for cross-repo visibility
since the original devmap predates them.


! instantiated-by: Prototype 12 — Social Pipeline & Agency [➰/双 🌽/末]
  :maturity :active
  :owner :futon3c
  :actual-status :active
  :depends-on []
  :implemented-as [futon3c/src/futon3c/social/*.clj + futon3c/src/futon3c/agency/*.clj]
  :evidence-for-active [5-stage pipeline wired and tested; agency registry operational; alleycat P-4 inhabitation race 20/20; all tech debt resolved (I3, coerce-prompt, hop exit inference)]

  + context: futon3c's core is the social pipeline: the real-time coordination path that agents traverse on every interaction.
  + IF: You want structured, typed coordination with evidence emission at every step
  + HOWEVER: Without a pipeline, agent interactions are ad-hoc function calls with no audit trail
  + THEN: Implement a 5-stage pipeline (S-presence → S-authenticate → S-mode → S-dispatch → S-persist) with Malli shape validation, agency registry with session lifecycle, and evidence emission on coordination events
  + BECAUSE: The pipeline is the social-timescale AIF loop: sense agent presence, validate credentials, resolve mode, dispatch to capability envelope, persist coordination evidence

  + EVIDENCE:
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/social/shapes.clj: ~550 lines, Malli shapes for all social types]
    evidence[holes/completed-mission-summaries.md: M-agency-unified-routing — single-JVM agent routing baseline that this pipeline operationalizes]
    evidence[holes/completed-mission-summaries.md: M-social-exotype — verified social loop + composition constraints that anchor this prototype]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/social/{presence,authenticate,mode,dispatch,persist,validate}.clj: 5 pipeline stages]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/social/bells.clj: bell dispatcher (standup bell + test bell, 12 tests)]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/agency/registry.clj: multi-agent registry, session lifecycle]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/runtime/agents.clj: runtime API]
    evidence[futon3c alleycat P-4: peripheral inhabitation race 20/20 + 4 checkpoints]
    evidence[futon3c alleycat P-6: structural closure 479+ tests]
    evidence[futon3c: all social pipeline tech debt resolved (I3 snapshot, lossy coerce-prompt, hop exit inference)]

  + NEXT-STEPS:
