! instantiated-by: Prototype 13 — Evidence Landscape [➰/双 🍍/办]
  :maturity :active
  :owner :futon3c
  :actual-status :active
  :depends-on [f3/P12]
  :implemented-as [futon3c/src/futon3c/evidence/*.clj + futon1a HTTP API]
  :evidence-for-active [Evidence store operational with AtomBackend (ephemeral) and XtdbBackend (durable via futon1a); thread projection via reply chains; 7 evidence types; HTTP API for write/query/chain]

  + context: The evidence landscape is the shared medium for all three timescales. Social coordination events, mission snapshots, PSR/PUR/PAR records, and portfolio observations all flow into queryable evidence entries.
  + IF: You want a unified, typed, queryable record of everything that happens across the stack
  + HOWEVER: Without a shared evidence store, coordination events are scattered across atoms, logs, and markdown files
  + THEN: Implement EvidenceBackend protocol with pluggable backends (AtomBackend for tests, XtdbBackend for production via futon1a); provide append/query/reply-chain/fork APIs; support 7 evidence types and reply-chain threading
  + BECAUSE: The evidence landscape supersedes both the forum service and the war room — all coordination artifacts become queryable evidence entries with typed subjects, claims, and tags

  + EVIDENCE:
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/evidence/backend.clj: EvidenceBackend protocol + AtomBackend]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/evidence/store.clj: append/query/reply-chain/fork API (~300 lines)]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/evidence/threads.clj: thread projection from reply chains]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/evidence/xtdb_backend.clj: XTDB persistence via futon1a]
    evidence[futon1a HTTP API: POST/GET /api/alpha/evidence, GET /evidence/:id, GET /evidence/:id/chain]
    evidence[EvidenceEntry shape: id, subject (ArtifactRef), type, claim-type, author, at, body, tags, reply-chain, forks]
    evidence[7 evidence types: pattern-selection, pattern-outcome, reflection, coordination, gate-traversal, forum-post, conjecture]
    evidence[Forum service OBSOLETE — superseded by evidence landscape]

  + NEXT-STEPS:
    next[M-forum-refactor: complete Parts II-IV for evidence-store invariants, thread projection, and S-validate integration]
    next[holes/non-completed-mission-summaries.md: M-forum-refactor - evidence landscape mission remains active (Part I ready; Parts II-IV blocked)]
    next[Add :query/subject-type filter to EvidenceQuery (gap G4 from mission-control VERIFY)]
    next[Connect futon3b proof-paths as evidence entries]
    next[Wire Arxana Lab viewer (futon4) to evidence endpoints]

  :success-criteria
    pass[Evidence entries appendable and queryable with typed subjects and claims]
    pass[Reply chains and thread projections operational]
    pass[XTDB backend provides durable persistence via futon1a]
    pass[Forum service obsoleted — evidence landscape handles all coordination artifacts]
    fail[Coordination events are unstructured or unqueryable]


! instantiated-by: Prototype 14 — Peripheral Runtime [🌽/末 ➰/广]
  :maturity :active
  :owner :futon3c
  :actual-status :active
  :depends-on [f3/P12, f3/P13]
  :implemented-as [futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/*.clj]
  :evidence-for-active [11 peripherals (10 wired, 1 shaped); PeripheralRunner protocol with start/step/stop lifecycle; hop-based transitions with explicit exit conditions; chain orchestration; evidence emission at every step; backward verification framework]

  + context: Peripherals are capability envelopes — each constrains what an agent can do and emits evidence of what it did.
  + IF: You want agents to operate within structured, auditable capability boundaries
  + HOWEVER: Without capability envelopes, agents have unrestricted access and produce no structured audit trail
  + THEN: Implement PeripheralRunner protocol (start/step/stop) with tool-set enforcement, hop-based transitions between peripherals, chain orchestration for multi-peripheral sequences, and evidence emission on every tool invocation
  + BECAUSE: Peripherals are the enforcement mechanism for the social AIF loop — they constrain agent actions to declared tool sets while producing linked evidence chains

  + EVIDENCE:
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/runner.clj: PeripheralRunner protocol]
    evidence[holes/completed-mission-summaries.md: M-psr-pur-mesh-peripheral — discipline envelope with PSR/PUR hop semantics]
    evidence[holes/completed-mission-summaries.md: M-alfworld-pattern-discovery — ALFWorld loop produced reusable patterns via peripheral execution]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/tools.clj: ToolBackend protocol + dispatch]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/common.clj: shared helpers (action validation, spec loading)]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/evidence.clj: evidence emission helpers]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/registry.clj: factory dispatch + chain orchestration]
    evidence[futon3c/src/futon3c/peripheral/round_trip.clj: backward verification (←) framework]
    evidence[futon3c/resources/peripherals.edn: 11 peripheral specs with tools, scope, entry/exit]
    evidence[10 wired: explore, edit, test, deploy, reflect, proof, discipline, mission, mission-control, alfworld]
    evidence[1 shaped: chat (IRC bridge fills role in practice)]

  + NEXT-STEPS:
    next[M-peripheral-gauntlet: execute real-time multi-peripheral scenarios across the 8-gate gauntlet; VERIFY work still pending]
    next[holes/non-completed-mission-summaries.md: M-peripheral-gauntlet - ARGUE complete, VERIFY pending with outstanding gate demonstrations]
    next[Wire chat peripheral implementation (or confirm IRC bridge suffices)]

  :success-criteria
    pass[11 peripheral specs defined with tool sets, scope, entry/exit conditions]
    pass[10 peripherals wired with PeripheralRunner implementations]
    pass[Hop transitions validated with explicit exit conditions]
    pass[Chain orchestration runs multi-peripheral sequences with evidence threading]
    pass[Backward verification framework validates structural invariants]
    fail[Agents bypass tool-set constraints or produce no evidence]


! instantiated-by: Prototype 15 — Transport Layer [➰/止 🌂/甲]
  :maturity :active
